## §2 · Sample constitution and bias

**11 V1.2 wild scans (entries 16–26)** — first scan 2026-04-20; last scan 2026-04-20.

### 2.1 Language/ecosystem coverage

| Language | Scans | Entries |
|---|---|---|
| Python | 2 | markitdown* + Kronos |
